name: In To The Blue
description:
Artwork Description:: 
Mixed media on canvas 610mm x 765mm Cost: 300

The Pesky Panda paints this piece to celebrate the anniversary of the Apollo 11 manned mission to land on the Moon on July 20, 1969. 

This is a real original painting by PeskyPanda; it is not a print of any kind digital or otherwise.  The painting is in high-grade acrylic paint varnished with a matt spray varnish, on a pure cotton box canvas.  The sides of the canvas are painted with a wrap around effect, no nails or staples and ready to hang.

This painting will delight the viewer is signed and comes with "Certificate of Authenticity"
